Class SignatureObjectInputStream

java.lang.Object
java.io.InputStream
java.io.ObjectInputStream
org.codehaus.mojo.animal_sniffer.SignatureObjectInputStream
All Implemented Interfaces:
Closeable, DataInput, ObjectInput, ObjectStreamConstants, AutoCloseable
public class SignatureObjectInputStream extends ObjectInputStream
ObjectInputStream subclass which only permits loading classes which are needed by signature files. All other classes are rejected for security reasons.
